<%= render "landing" %>

<div class="what-container">
  <div class="what-grids">
    <div class="panel-03">
      <h1>What<br> is this about?</h1>
      <%= image_tag "blob_green03.png", alt: "blob", width: "150px", class: "blob-what-green" %>
      <%= image_tag "blob_pink03.png", alt: "blob", width: "80px", class: "blob-what-pink" %>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-04">
      <p>
      What is this web site all about? How did you get here?
      Maybe subconsciously you were thirsty for a drink!

      <br><br>

      Free Pour Cocktail is a place where you can find
      the perfect recipe for the drink you're looking for.
      It can be as simple as a classic Daiquiri or discover
      someone else's creation! What ever mood you're in, you'll find something to match it here.

      <br><br>

      Enjoy and drink responsibly. Cheers!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="banner-image">
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cocktail-container">

  <div class="cocktail-title">
    <h1>= Cocktails =</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="cocktail-list">
    <div id="column-01"></div>
    <div>
      <div class="cocktail-info">
        <div class="cocktail-search">
          <p>view:</p>
          <p>spirit</p>
          <p>rating</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cocktail-cards">
        
          <% @cocktails.order('lower(name)').each do |cocktail| %>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-title">
                <h3><%= cocktail.name.capitalize %></h3>
              </div>
              <div class="card-image">
                <% if cocktail.tag %>
                  <%= image_tag "#{cocktail.tag}", alt: "#{cocktail.name}" %>
                <% else %>
                  <%= image_tag "cocktail_card.jpg", alt: "#{cocktail.name}" %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
              <div class="card-rating">
                <p class="stars"><%= "âœ©" * cocktail.rating %></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div id="column-03"></div>
  </div>
</div>

